cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use KUREAS in your work, please cite it using the metadata below.

title: >
  KUREAS: Knowledgebase with Uncertainty for Risk Engineering Analysis of Systems

abstract: >
  KUREAS is an open-source, browser-based suite of single-file
  HTML applications for probabilistic risk assessment (PRA) and
  reliability engineering in nuclear and industrial safety
  contexts. The suite targets SAPHIRE compatibility and is
  designed for use in DOE Safety Analysis Documents and similar
  regulatory environments. Modules include fault-tree and
  event-tree editors, hazard analysis, system evaluation with
  importance measures and common-cause failure modeling, 3-D
  facility visualization, sequence analysis, external hazard
  risk analysis, a knowledge-base container, a report generator,
  and a general-purpose utility suite. All modules run entirely
  in the browser with no build step and no server requirement.

